{"id":151011,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/苹果雇员被指殴打ipad-2买家/","date":"2011-05-09T10:00:41Z","modified":"2011-05-09T10:00:41Z","title":"苹果雇员被指殴打iPad 2买家","content":"<p>《北京晨报》和AFP报导(视频)，北京三里屯苹果店昨天下午发生了打斗事故，有4人在事故中受伤。一位“外籍”苹果雇员被指冲进iPad 2排队人群中，殴打一位被怀疑插队的顾客，之后的混乱总共导致4人受伤，苹果店内一扇玻璃门破碎，并因此暂停营业。据《法制日报》报道，周日上午10时，三里屯苹果专卖店恢复了运营，打人的外籍男子确为苹果专卖店的员工，双方已就赔偿事宜达成一致。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14ac279f/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E9%9B%87%E5%91%98%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%AE%B4%E6%89%93iPad+2%E4%B9%B0%E5%AE%B6&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fapple.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F08%2F0722250%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E9%9B%87%E5%91%98%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%AE%B4%E6%89%93iPad+2%E4%B9%B0%E5%AE%B6&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fapple.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F08%2F0722250%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091662518/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14ac279f/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091662518/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14ac279f/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=Tnl-pd9W-KE:4cLU6AXz5NI:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=Tnl-pd9W-KE:4cLU6AXz5NI:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息